data.description: OPEN HOUSE - NEXT WEEK --> SUNDAY 5/5/24 2-4pm. *** THIS WILL NOT LAST LONG !  Amazing 4 bed/2 bath/2 car home on a large 1/2 acre lot in Newcastle.  This home has been maintained immaculantly and used recently as a AirBnB, when owners were relocated.  Reserved appliances can be included with a full purchase price offer.  Other household decor items can be negotiated and added on top of purchase price, if buyer desires.  This home is minutes from Tri City Shopping area, I44 to OKC or Blanchard and SH9 to Norman.  Current photos show how big this home is.  Professional photos coming shortly.  VA loan transfer is an opportunity, if buyer desires and qualifies for.  Garage has a slot inside cut out for a storm shelter to easily be inserted by the new owners, but does not have a shelter currently.  HOA is $200 annually for greenbelt maintenance.  Shown by appointment only through ShowingTime/Sentri.
